        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2276679739" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7068178796520251067">Another book that I loved. Really good, historical story about the woman who started the phrase &quot;A Diamond is forever&quot; for DeBeers back in the 1940&apos;s and also a story about one special engagement ring that went through 4 generations and the people that owned it. Would definitely recommend this. I love historical fiction and also a good drama!</span>
  <span id="freeText7068178796520251067" style="display:none">Another book that I loved. Really good, historical story about the woman who started the phrase "A Diamond is forever" for DeBeers back in the 1940's and also a story about one special engagement ring that went through 4 generations and the people that owned it. Would definitely recommend this. I love historical fiction and also a good drama!</span>
