<span id="freeTextContainer9507117436243051748">I read the first 80 pages and just couldn&apos;t stop hating it. Like a girl from Belmont watched an episode of Mad Men and turned it into an icky derivative mess. Perhaps I was just in a cruel mood, but no. I don&apos;t believe your Boston characters, I don&apos;t believe your Philly characters. And I do believe your obsession with marriage is troubling.</span>
  <span id="freeText9507117436243051748" style="display:none">I read the first 80 pages and just couldn't stop hating it. Like a girl from Belmont watched an episode of Mad Men and turned it into an icky derivative mess. Perhaps I was just in a cruel mood, but no. I don't believe your Boston characters, I don't believe your Philly characters. And I do believe your obsession with marriage is troubling.</span>
